 {"id":"bd-1w8f","title":"Ingest NTM robot alerts + mail into gateway snapshot","description":"Goal:\n- Integrate NTM robot alerts/mail into gateway alerting + snapshot.\n\nScope:\n- `ntm --robot-alerts` → gateway alerts.\n- `ntm --robot-mail` → snapshot mail section (read-only).\n\nDefinition of Done:\n- Snapshot includes NTM alerts/mail summaries.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-21T04:48:36.183109390Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-21T21:02:16.994072140Z","closed_at":"2026-01-21T21:02:16.993971731Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["ntm","snapshot"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1w8f","depends_on_id":"bd-284u","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-21T04:48:36.352719211Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-1w8f","depends_on_id":"bd-29in","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-21T04:52:03.084987081Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-1w8f","depends_on_id":"bd-2h6i","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-21T04:51:57.240721215Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
 {"id":"bd-1w9e","title":"Manifest fallback + user-facing error messaging","description":"Goal:\n- Ensure graceful fallback when ACFS manifest is missing/invalid.\n\nScope:\n- Provide minimal built-in registry with core tools.\n- Emit user-facing errors with actionable guidance.\n- Include structured logs with manifest path + error category.\n\nTests / Verification (detailed logging required):\n- Unit/Integration: bd-1kkl (fallback behavior + error paths).\n\nDefinition of Done:\n- /setup endpoints function with fallback and clear diagnostics.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-21T05:45:36.434749511Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-23T08:14:14.967874162Z","closed_at":"2026-01-23T08:14:14.967693682Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["acfs","registry","ux"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1w9e","depends_on_id":"bd-1hac","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-21T05:45:36.466557092Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-1w9e","depends_on_id":"bd-ka28","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-21T05:45:57.114124636Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
